<h1><a href="../">Perl Advent Calendar 2010-12</a>-8++</h1>
<h2 align="center">Selfless gifting</h2>
<h3 align="center">by Jerrad Pierce</h3>
<p>Given the megamiles of ribbon Nick goes through every December, it should come as no surprise that he's not a afraid of <tt>tie</tt>ing the occasional package from time to time. He therefore had no aversion to the labor saving design of <tt><a href="http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?selfvars">selfvars</a></tt>, a module that simplifies the tedious accessing of method parameters.</p>
<a name="mod8.pl" id="mod8.pl"></a><h2><a href="mod8.pl">mod8.pl</a></h2><pre>
<a name="package-Present"></a>   1 <span class="k">package </span><span class="i">Present</span><span class="sc">;</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.2"></a>   2 <span class="k">use</span> <span class="w">selfvars</span><span class="sc">;</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.3"></a>   3 
<a name="new"></a>   4 <span class="k">sub </span><span class="m">new</span><span class="s">{</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.5"></a>   5     <span class="k">return</span> <span class="k">bless</span><span class="s">(</span><span class="s">{</span><span class="s">}</span><span class="cm">,</span> <span class="k">shift</span><span class="s">)</span><span class="sc">;</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.6"></a>   6 <span class="s">}</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.7"></a>   7 
<a name="give"></a>   8 <span class="k">sub </span><span class="m">give</span><span class="s">{</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.9"></a>   9     <span class="c">#Look ma! No shift</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.10"></a>  10     <span class="k">printf</span> <span class="q">&quot;%s to %s\n&quot;</span><span class="cm">,</span> <span class="i">$hopts</span>{<span class="w">what</span>}<span class="cm">,</span> <span class="i">$hopts</span>{<span class="w">who</span>}<span class="sc">;</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.11"></a>  11 <span class="s">}</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.12"></a>  12 
<a name="package-main"></a>  13 <span class="k">package </span><span class="i">main</span><span class="sc">;</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.14"></a>  14 
<a name="mod8.pl.15"></a>  15 <span class="k">my</span> <span class="i">$gift</span> = <span class="w">new</span> <span class="w">Present</span><span class="sc">;</span>
<a name="mod8.pl.16"></a>  16 <span class="i">$gift</span><span class="i">-&gt;give</span><span class="s">(</span><span class="w">what</span><span class="cm">=&gt;</span><span class="q">&#39;Zoozit sticks&#39;</span><span class="cm">,</span> <span class="w">who</span><span class="cm">=&gt;</span><span class="q">&#39;Cindy Lou&#39;</span><span class="s">)</span><span class="sc">;</span>
</pre>
